  "text": "Lateral semicircular canal type BPPV was more common in sudden SNHL patients with BPPV [CITATION_1] . However, we found no significant difference among BPPV types. Lee and Ban [CITATION_2] reported that subtypes of BPPV couldn't influence on the hearing outcome, just reflect serious labyrinthine damage on canals.",
